  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Ice Cream</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/32px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Ice Cream</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Items\" title=\"Items\">Item</a> in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i> DLC. It is cooked in a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dairy product\">Dairy product</a>, and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\">Sweetener</a>.\n</p><p>No <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetables\">Vegetables</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a>, or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a> can be added. <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruits\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruits</a> are an acceptable filler.\n</p><p>Ice Cream gives a boost of 50 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/20px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a> when eaten, the highest of all Food items, tied with <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lobster_Dinner\" title=\"Lobster Dinner\">Lobster Dinner</a> from the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Jelly_Salad\" title=\"Jelly Salad\">Jelly Salad</a> from <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>. It restores 25 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/20px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a> and no <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/20px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>. In addition, it decreases the player&#x27;s temperature by 1 degree per second for 15 seconds when consumed, this can make it useful for the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Summer#Reign_of_Giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a>, when <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Overheating\" title=\"Overheating\">Overheating</a> is a constant threat.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Downloadable_Content\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gift_Icon\" title=\"Gift Icon\"><img alt=\"Gift Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Gift_Icon.png/32px-Gift_Icon.png?8b4efa\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Downloadable Content</span></h2>\n<p>Ice Cream is also included in the <i>Shipwrecked</i> DLC, as Ice can be obtained by using an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Maker_3000\" title=\"Ice Maker 3000\">Ice Maker 3000</a>, or by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Refine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Refine\">Refining</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hail\" title=\"Hail\">Hail</a>. It can be used to deal with Overheating during the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seasons/Dry\" title=\"Seasons/Dry\">Dry Season</a> or Sanity loss caused by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wetness\" title=\"Wetness\">Wetness</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" title=\"Dairy product\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot.png?bb1767\" width=\"580\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs_Crock_Pot.png?afac2d\" width=\"175\" height=\"82\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot.png?fc26f1\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" title=\"Dairy product\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream\" title=\"Ice Cream\"><img alt=\"Ice Cream.pn