class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" title=\"Dairy product\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cave_Bananas\" title=\"Cave Bananas\"><img alt=\"Bananas.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Bananas.png?6e67ce\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream\" title=\"Ice Cream\"><img alt=\"Ice Cream.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice_Cream.png?1312fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Tools.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream\" title=\"Ice Cream\"><img alt=\"Ice Cream.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice_Cream.png?1312fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Icon\" title=\"Pig Icon\"><img alt=\"Pig Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pig_Icon.png/42px-Pig_Icon.png?2561d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Manure\" title=\"Manure\"><img alt=\"Manure.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Manure.png?f3cf48\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream\" title=\"Ice Cream\"><img alt=\"Ice Cream.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice_Cream.png?1312fc\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Usher\" title=\"Pig Usher\"><img alt=\"Pig Usher.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pig_Usher.png/42px-Pig_Usher.png?b5f62c\" width=\"42\" height=\"64\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oinc\" title=\"Oinc\"><img alt=\"Oinc.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Oinc.png?bf1bac\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Ice_Cream_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Ice_Cream_128x128.png/120px-Ice_Cream_128x128.png?bc2265\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/32px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Tips</span></h2>\n<ul><li>The player can eat Ice Cream during <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seasons/Summer\" title=\"Seasons/Summer\">Summer</a> to lower their temperature. It can be an alternative to Luxury Fan when the player needs <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\">Hunger</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\">Sanity</a>.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
