  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nExclusive to:\nIce Cream\nFood Info\n25\n0\n50\nVeggie\nObject Info\nPerk\nLowers temperature by 15 degrees over 15 seconds.\n3 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x1 x1\n10 sec\n10\nMiscellaneous\n\"icecream\"\n“I scream for ice cream!”\n–Wilson\n“Well, soooometimes cold things are okay.”\n–Willow\n“Well, is Sunday after all.”\n–Wolfgang\n“Ice cream could never replace Abigail.”\n–Wendy\n“SWEET DAIRY”\n–WX-78\n“Nothing like a book and a bowl of ice cream.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Only after I've chopped enough!”\n–Woodie\n“Sundae, sundae, sundae!”\n–Maxwell\n“Happily, ice cream tastes the same here.”\n–Wagstaff\n“It hurts my teeth.”\n–Wigfrid\n“We dream of ice cream.”\n–Webber\n“Perfect treat to pair with a hammock in the sun.”\n–Walani\n“The heat is sweetly beat!”\n–Warly\n“Refreshin' on a hot day.”\n–Woodlegs\n“WILBA SCREAM'TH FOR ICE CREAM'TH”\n–Wilba\n“Cool”\n–Wormwood\n“I'm going to eat this so fast I'll get an ice cream headache!”\n–Wheeler\n“Y'gotta eat it before it melts.”\n–Winona\n“I could probably stomach that.”\n–Wortox\n“Cold treat!”\n–Wurt\n“Don't eat too much or you'll get a stomach ache.”\n–Walter\n“Alright, maybe just a bowl or two.”\n–Wanda\nIce Cream is a Food Item in the Reign of Giants DLC. It is cooked in a Crock Pot by combining 1 Ice, 1 Dairy product, and 1 Sweetener.\nNo Meats, Vegetables, Eggs, or Twigs can be added. Fruits are an acceptable filler.\nIce Cream gives a boost of 50 when eaten, the highest of all Food items, tied with Lobster Dinner from the Shipwrecked DLC and Jelly Salad from Don't Starve Together. It restores 25 and no . In addition, it decreases the player's temperature by 1 degree per second for 15 seconds when consumed, this can make it useful for the Summer, when Overheating is a constant threat.\nDownloadable Content[edit | edit source]\nIce Cream is also included in the Shipwrecked DLC, as Ice can be obtained by using an Ice Maker 3000, or by Refining Hail. It can be used to deal with Overheating during the Dry Season or Sanity loss caused by Wetness.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nExcludes:\nExcludes:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\nExamples[edit | edit source]\nA recipe for Ice Cream that extenuates hunger value\n×2\n×2\nUsage[edit | edit source]\n×4\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\nTips[edit | edit source]\nThe player can eat Ice Cream during Summer to lower their temperature. It can be an alternative to Luxury Fan when the player needs Hunger and Sanity.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
