  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Exclusivity|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|foodType = [[Veggie]] [[File:Veggie.png|32px|]]\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Ice}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Dairy product}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Sweetener}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1\n|icon = Ice Cream.png\n|image = Ice Cream Dropped.png\n|hpRestored = 0\n|canBeBurned=1\n|hungerRestored = 25\n|sanityRestored = 50\n|crafting = Cooked in a [[Crock Pot]]\n|cooktime = 10 sec\n|priority = 10\n|spoil = 3 Days\n|stack = 40\n|spawnCode = \"icecream\"\n|perk = Lowers temperature by 15 degrees over 15 seconds.\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = I scream for ice cream!\n|willow = Well, soooometimes cold things are okay.\n|wolfgang = Well, is Sunday after all.\n|wendy = Ice cream could never replace Abigail.\n|wx78 = SWEET DAIRY\n|wickerbottom = Nothing like a book and a bowl of ice cream.\n|woodie = Only after I've chopped enough!\n|maxwell = Sundae, sundae, sundae!\n|wagstaff = Happily, ice cream tastes the same here.\n|wigfrid = It hurts my teeth.\n|webber = We dream of ice cream.\n|walani = Perfect treat to pair with a hammock in the sun.\n|warly = The heat is sweetly beat!\n|woodlegs = Refreshin' on a hot day.\n|wilba = WILBA SCREAM'TH FOR ICE CREAM'TH\n|wormwood = Cool\n|wheeler = I'm going to eat this so fast I'll get an ice cream headache!\n|winona = Y'gotta eat it before it melts.\n|wortox = I could probably stomach that.\n|wurt = Cold treat!\n|walter = Don't eat too much or you'll get a stomach ache.\n|wanda = Alright, maybe just a bowl or two.\n|choose = webber\n}}\n'''Ice Cream''' is a [[Food]] [[Items|Item]] in the ''[[Don't Starve: Reign of Giants|Reign of Giants]]'' DLC. It is cooked in a [[Crock Pot]] by combining 1 [[Ice]], 1 [[Dairy product]], and 1 [[Sweetener]].\n\nNo [[Meats]], [[Vegetables]], [[Eggs]], or [[Twigs]] can be added. [[Fruits]] are an acceptable filler.\n\nIce Cream gives a boost of 50 {{sanity}} when eaten, the highest of all Food items, tied with [[Lobster Dinner]] from the ''[[Don't Starve: Shipwrecked|Shipwrecked]]'' DLC and [[Jelly Salad]] from ''[[Don't Starve Together]]''. It restores 25 {{Hunger}} and no {{Hp}}. In addition, it decreases the player's temperature by 1 degree per second for 15 seconds when consumed, this can make it useful for the [[Summer#Reign of Giants|Summer]], when [[Overheating]] is a constant threat.\n== {{Pic32|Gift Icon}} Downloadable Content ==\nIce Cream is also included in the ''Shipwrecked'' DLC, as Ice can be obtained by using an [[Ice Maker 3000]], or by [[Refine|Refining]] [[Hail]]. It can be used to deal with Overheating during the [[Seasons/Dry|Dry Season]] or Sanity loss caused by [[Wetness]].\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Ice.png|link=Ice]]\n* Requires: [[File:Dairy product.png|link=Dairy product]]\n* Requires: [[File:Sweetener.png|link=Sweetener]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Meats Crock Pot.png|link=Meats]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Eggs Crock Pot.png|link=Eggs]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Vegetables Crock Pot.png|link=Vegetables]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Twigs.png|link=Twigs]]\n\n== [[File:Cookbook.png|32px|link=]] Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice\n|item2 = Dairy product\n|item3 = Sweetener\n|item4 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Ice Cream\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe|item1=Electric Milk|item2=Honey|item3=Ice|item4=Ice|pot=yes|result=Ice Cream|note={{Pic24|Prototype}} A recipe for Ice Cream that extenuates hunger value}}{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice\n|item2 = Dairy product\n|item3 = Sweetener\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Ice Cream\n|count1=2}}{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice\n|item2 = Dairy product\n|item3 = Sweetener\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Ice Cream\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice\n|item2 = Dairy product\n|item3 = Sweetener\n|item4 = Berry\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Ice Cream\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice\n|item2 = Dairy product\n|item3 = Sweetener\n|item4 = Cave Bananas\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Ice Cream\n}}\n== [[File:Icon Tools.png|32px]] Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice Cream\n|tool = Pig Icon\n|result = Manure\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Ice Cream\n|tool = Pig Usher\n|result = Oinc\n|resultcount = 4\n|dlc = Hamlet\n}}\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nIce Cream 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n\n== {{Pic32|Prototype}} Tips ==\n* The player can eat Ice Cream during [[Seasons/Summer|Summer]] to lower their temperature. It can be an alternative to Luxury Fan when the player needs [[Hunger]] and [[Sanity]].\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n\n__NOTOC__\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Cooling]]\n[[Category:Shipwrecked]]\n\n[[fr: crème glacée]]\n[[pl:Lody (RoG)]]\n[[ru:Мороженое]]\n[[zh:冰淇淋]]"
